%h1 Using the CLI

%p
  Once you install Mint you will have a
  %code mint
  binary at your disposal.

%p
  This is the help section (you can print this using the
  %code --help
  flag):

%pre
  %code.plaintext
    :plain
      mint --help
      Mint - Help
